    <item>
      <title>德意志银行的 Uleer：仍有理由继续看好欧洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/deutsche-bank-still-reason-to-remain-bullish-on-europe-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行的 Maximilian Uleer 表示，尽管最近欧洲投资前景不容乐观，但仍有理由保持乐观。他预测欧洲消费支出和房地产将复苏，尤其看好英国。他在《彭博：开盘交易》节目中与 Anna Edwards、Kriti Gupta 和 Lizzy Burden 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/deutsche-bank-still-reason-to-remain-bullish-on-europe-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 08:37:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰铢波动，比索在降息后保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/baht-fluctuates-peso-treads-water-after-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行出乎投资者意料地宣布四年多来首次降息，泰铢汇率随之大幅波动。菲律宾央行按预期降息后，菲律宾比索几乎没有变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/baht-fluctuates-peso-treads-water-after-interest-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 08:27:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国通胀低于预期促使交易员加大降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/uk-inflation-falls-more-than-forecast-to-1-7-lowest-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通胀率三年多来首次跌破英国央行 2% 的目标，促使投资者押注未来几个月英国央行将加快降息步伐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/uk-inflation-falls-more-than-forecast-to-1-7-lowest-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 06:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行不断向客户投入数十亿美元，威胁雨林</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/banks-keep-plowing-billions-into-clients-threatening-rainforests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究表明，银行和资产管理公司正继续向那些业务直接威胁亚马逊等热带雨林未来的公司投入数百亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/banks-keep-plowing-billions-into-clients-threatening-rainforests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 03:31:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ASML 销售预警后，全球芯片股市值蒸发 4200 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/global-chip-stocks-shed-420-billion-as-asml-shock-halts-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于主要设备供应商阿斯麦控股公司（ASML Holding NV）的不温不火的前景引发全球芯片行业崩溃，芯片股投资者正面临新的考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/global-chip-stocks-shed-420-billion-as-asml-shock-halts-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 02:52:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因盈利疲软而下跌；英镑下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市下跌，因为奢侈品行业盈利疲软加剧了人们对半导体行业盈利前景的负面情绪。由于英国通胀率下降刺激人们对降息的押注增加，英镑下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 22:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁阿加瓦尔为债券市场忠实投资者带来 98% 的涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/billionaire-anil-agarwal-s-vedanta-delivers-98-rally-to-debt-market-faithful</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金属价格上涨、融资环境改善以及印度对垃圾债投资者的吸引力不断增加，这些都为 Anil Agarwal 的韦丹塔公司带来了帮助。但挑战依然存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/billionaire-anil-agarwal-s-vedanta-delivers-98-rally-to-debt-market-faithful</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 21:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
